                testParams.shortAmount
            );
            (, int256 expectedShortProceeds) = HyperdriveUtils
                .calculateCompoundInterest(
                    testParams.shortAmount,
                    testParams.variableRate,
                    POSITION_DURATION
                );
            assertApproxEqAbs(
                shortProceeds,
                uint256(expectedShortProceeds),
